                    <span>Not being familliar with Ambrose's work, we're not sure if all his books are written like like this, but it seems that he was padding the text to be paid by the word!  Repetitions of entire blocks of text, while admittedly properly footnoted and/or indexed give the book the feel of a report written by a highschooler.</span>
                  
